<text evidence="5">Cells lacking this gene show a reduced growth rate at high butanol concentrations compared to wild-type. They also show a consistent change in the level of mannitol, D-sorbitol, galactitol, L-tyrosine, 3-amino-3-(4-hydroxyphenyl)propanoate and N-hydroxy-L-phenylalanine.</text>
</comment>
